1
00:01:03,091 --> 00:01:06,760
[Episode 17]

2
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:14,439
Your Highness,
it has been thoroughly investigated.

3
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:17,359
It was Xiao Chen who conducted
a private investigation on Wen Churan.

4
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,560
What has he found out?

5
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,608
He has found a witness.

6
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:25,400
It seems that we cannot keep
the Wen family anymore.

7
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,519
The maid said you wanted to see me.

8
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:52,200
So, have you come around
to becoming my Crown Princess?

9
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,480
I've come around for a long time.

10
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:58,319
Weren't you the one who dodged away that day?

11
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:04,680
Tell me, who else is there?

12
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:07,840
I, your younger brother, have learned
that today is your birthday.

13
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:10,639
I came to offer my congratulations
to my imperial brother.

14
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:16,400
It seems you've all planned this well.

15
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,000
What's your purpose?

16
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,039
What's the rush? We have more people to join.

17
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:32,080
Your Highness.

18
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,719
What are you trying to do?

19
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:36,240
In the previous life, we crossed swords.

20
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:39,319
In the end, we separated in life and death.

21
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:41,680
In this life, why don't we fulfill
each other's wishes

22
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:47,000
to live in peace from now on.

23
00:02:52,467 --> 00:02:57,160
[Divorce Agreement]

24
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:06,400
Go and fetch my brush and ink.

25
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:09,064
Yes.

26
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:21,256
Divorce…

27
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:27,280
Divorce?! You already know about
what happened with the Wen family.

28
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,560
You will certainly not let me go.

29
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,639
Likewise, I will not let you go either.

30
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:36,599
Alright. Let's see whose people can act faster.

31
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,360
This is the Eastern Palace!

32
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,840
If this were not the Eastern Palace,

33
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:48,599
your schemes would be of no use.

34
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:51,960
Guards, drag him in for me.

35
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:54,056
Yes.

36
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,520
The prince of Qinglan…

37
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:10,800
The Crown Prince's collusion with Qinglan
is irrefutable.

38
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:14,159
Do you have anything else you want to say?

39
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:17,000
Sun Cheng, you traitor!

40
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,519
I am going to kill him after I kill you all.

41
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:23,199
Do you think you still have a chance?

42
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:27,000
In the previous life, I failed to kill you.

43
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,600
Today, I will make you disappear from Da'an.

44
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:32,240
Why must you wipe out the Wen family?

45
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:40,519
Do you know how I came about
the position of the Crown Prince?

46
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:48,399
In order to make me the Crown Prince,
my royal father

47
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:50,480
not only granted death to my birth mother,

48
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,959
but also exiled my uncle's family.

49
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:57,240
If I do not perform well
on the throne of Crown Prince,

50
00:04:57,240 --> 00:05:00,040
how could I live up to my mother's sacrifice?

51
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,639
How could I vindicate my uncle?

52
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:04,079
That's why you colluded with Qinglan,

53
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:06,040
and sold the purple gold to Qinglan.

54
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,199
Do you know that these purple gold

55
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:09,279
will ultimately be used
against the people of Da'an!

56
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:13,720
Qinglan is such a tiny place!

57
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,800
After I ascend to the throne,

58
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:19,800
I will certainly eradicate Qinglan,

59
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:23,160
and the purple gold will surely return
to my Da'an.

60
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,920
Then how dare you make a move
against the Wen family?

61
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,079
If something happens to the Wen family,

62
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:30,120
even before your enthronement,

63
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:34,319
Da'an would be trampled
by the cavalry of Qinglan!

64
00:05:34,319 --> 00:05:36,639
That's utterly ridiculous!

65
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:43,639
Xiao Heng, the news of your exposure

66
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:47,480
should be here any minute.

67
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:50,360
The imperial edict is here!

68
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,720
The Emperor has issued a decree.

69
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:57,319
The Crown Prince Xiao Heng,
colluded with the enemy and committed treason,

70
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:59,120
[Hall of Yanming]
intended to execute court officials,

71
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,600
unable to tell right from wrong,
greatly disappointing the people.

72
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:04,720
Hereby bestow a cup of poisoned wine
to demonstrate imperial grace.

73
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,839
Decree by the Emperor.

74
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:11,639
It's fake, it's fake!

75
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,848
Your Highness!

76
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:42,240
Your Highness, Your Highness.

77
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:46,720
Your Highness, Your Highness.

78
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,704
Your Highness.

79
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:55,040
Your Highness, you go first.

80
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:59,519
I will surely

81
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,120
live on well for you.

82
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:23,008
What are you doing?

83
00:08:23,008 --> 00:08:25,032
[How to make your lady love you more]

84
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,879
What's this?

85
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:30,040
I-It's nothing.

86
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,072
Let me see.

87
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:36,168
Let me see!

88
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,656
Let me take a look--

89
00:08:50,039 --> 00:08:53,159
Let me take a look. Let me take a look!

90
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,032
Are you okay?

91
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,928
I won.

92
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:06,600
Y-You tricked me?

93
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:09,512
Are you angry?

94
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:13,639
Yes, I'm angry.

95
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,960
You are generous.

96
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,360
Give me a chance to make it up to you.

97
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,519
How do you plan to show sincerity?

98
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:47,519
You can buy as much as you want.

99
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,519
So, this is your promise.

100
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:56,799
I meant the stall over there.

101
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:03,120
Y-You're a prince after all.

102
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,120
A prince needs to eat as well.

103
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,879
The past was always full of
fighting and killing.

104
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:17,939
Life has finally quieted down a bit now.

105
00:10:17,939 --> 00:10:22,440
I just want to spend simple days with you.

106
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,464
Just like them.

107
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:33,120
I'll make your favorite dish
when we get home today.

108
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,759
Really? Then I'm in for a treat.

109
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:40,240
Fresh greens for sale at a low price!

110
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,919
Miss, come take a look!

111
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:44,576
Come take a look, Miss.

112
00:10:44,576 --> 00:10:47,200
Three coins a catty, very fresh!

113
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,352
Three coins a catty.

114
00:10:58,323 --> 00:10:59,200
[How to make your lady love you more]

115
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,480
To capture her heart,

116
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:04,039
one must first capture her stomach.

117
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,080
Be careful.

118
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,320
Inside here are all my treasures.

119
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,440
Treasures?

120
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,640
[The talented and the beautiful]
What treasures?

121
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:18,240
I thought it was a martial arts manual.

122
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:21,759
A martial arts manual isn't
as important as this.

123
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:26,039
Your grandma and I were together
for a lifetime without ever fighting.

124
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:29,000
It's all thanks to this.

125
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,208
[How to make your lady love you more]
Grandfather!

126
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:35,440
You brat, study hard.

127
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,280
I will listen to grandfather's advice.

128
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:45,279
Grandfather, let me take you to the wing-room
to rest first.

129
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:49,448
Alright. Study hard.

130
00:11:53,043 --> 00:11:55,720
[How to make your lady love you more]

131
00:11:57,555 --> 00:12:02,408
[How to make your lady love you more]

